      • use

        public void use(Lattice.Column column,
                boolean measure)
        Records a use of a column.
        参数:
        column - Column
        measure - Whether this use is as an argument to a measure; e.g. "sum(x + y)" is a measure use of the expression "x + y"; "group by x + y" is not
